stringStats.value: Return this and the other nine artifacts to your Task Master to complete the quest.

A necklace made from the teeth of the monstrous Hagrafash. Long ago Hagrafash fed on our people and destroyed our great works. Our people could not fight such a beast as the Hagrafash and they suffered greatly. Then, from among the hunters came a savior, Baalfroth, to whom The Whispering One had bestowed great strength. He went forth and slew the great beast with only his spear.
